DTSTAMP:20260326T185921Z
UID:986312
DESCRIPTION:<p><em>Just In Time</em> is an &ldquo\;utterly electrifying&rd
 quo\; (<em>Entertainment Weekly</em>) new musical that brings to life the 
 story of Bobby Darin\, the legendary singer whose short but remarkable jou
 rney took him from teen idol to global sensation.<br /><br />Developed and
  directed by Tony Award&reg\; winner Alex Timbers (<em>Moulin Rouge!</em>)
 \, the show immerses audiences into an intimate nightclub &ldquo\;so seduc
 tive in ambiance that you find yourself not wanting to go back outside&rdq
 uo\; (<em>Chicago Tribune</em>). Complete with iconic hits including &ldqu
 o\;Beyond the Sea\,&rdquo\; &ldquo\;Mack the Knife\,&rdquo\; &ldquo\;Splis
 h Splash\,&rdquo\; and &ldquo\;Dream Lover\,&rdquo\; <em>Just In Time</em>
  is &ldquo\;a helluva good time at the theater&rdquo\; (<em>Time Out</em>)
 .</p>
LOCATION:Circle In The Square Theatre\, 1633 Broadway / 235 West 50th Stre
 et\, New York NY 10019
END:VEVENT
